{"tid":366363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人嘅衛生意識真係每況越下","createTime":"2017-08-20T03:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T16:36:02.000Z","uid":28802,"like":387,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d83d6237773e6f16cc5b04e481af70dadc8bc17a","tid":366363,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"覺得有必要開個post講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5月到依家因為流感而死嘅有300幾個人<br />\n呢幾個月身邊都好多人病咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得近呢兩三年 香港人嘅衛生常識減弱咗好多<br />\n好多廢老喺街喺地鐵打乞嚏都唔冚住 噴到周圍都係<br />\n其實用手臂去擋住都好啊 噴到人真係好影響到<br />\n如果真係病就戴番個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係成日見到啲人去完廁所唔洗手<br />\n呢樣野真係好撚唔衛生<br />\n摸完馬桶又剩咁污糟係咪應該洗手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨地吐痰就更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪要搞多鑊沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人永遠都要賴野去都人心惶惶嘅情況<br />\n先識去加強意識同做好預防措施 保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7562462a3c7adeb0e137e027a981457ab3af58","tid":366363,"uid":28802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41de8fbfbf75bc255bcd96ec43024ada48bdafa5","tid":366363,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"未入嚟已經估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b8f810774d724889ae183dec96a9f6a1a4932b","tid":366363,"uid":54733,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"廢老係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n呢班人冇得教"},{"pid":"6d9247956c24f30a35af29701e401121ff2fecc5","tid":366363,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy"