受教育真係可以好撚誇張，擺埋嗰副無動於衷嘅款真係嚇撚死人"},{"pid":"3f05fb9bff76fec221fa653c7dcce2b0a197bbb9","tid":366363,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"大陸人"},{"pid":"04c5d6c1cbd8b6b64638b45fb808093a9f70c044","tid":366363,"uid":75422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:24:22.000Z","msg":"依家仲有好撚多人<br />\n室內食煙 有蓋地方食煙 車站食煙<br />\n仲要煙頭丟落地下<br />\n以前都唔係咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌晒佢地老母"},{"pid":"d3084cd7c954460308c0c6e510adcf9cd5d7d1c7","tid":366363,"uid":75422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家仲有好撚多人<br />\n室內食煙 有蓋地方食煙 車站食煙<br />\n仲要煙頭丟落地下<br />\n以前都唔係咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌晒佢地老母</blockquote><br />\n雖然呢個post想講傳染病<br />\n但煙都係公共衛生問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf4964a3fcb5df757848b765bc86d140e03ea87","tid":366363,"uid":4349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:34:00.000Z","msg":"地鐵果d廢老, 你真係要隊個口罩比佢叫佢帶<br />\n<br />\n不過我無咁好心, 我會對空氣講仆街老坑咳都唔掩口<br />\n講到佢聽到果隻<br />\n通常會怒啤我, 比番個兇樣佢睇佢就收皮<br />\n呢d醜人係要有人做, 話佢佢地知咳係要掩口/帶口罩"},{"pid":"6fc3f47beb9c1d1c7c1dafa745a84343946f9d73","tid":366363,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搞清楚<br />\n沙士係當年支那人送大禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講野,你叫d5毛講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03533610e46c4832f229e17885bb9b4ace15f93e","tid":366363,"uid":80725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"我坐巴士尾二嗰行 最後排啲位咪會升高啲嘅<br />\n我後面個男人又肺癆又乞痴<br />\n好似啲菌飛哂落我個頭度咁<br />\n真係好怕搭巴士坐附近啲keke kamkam呀叔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bb447dd18d09e9875ebd61c39a7356d998e06b","tid":366363,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:54:41.000Z","msg":"講起就火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係呢班友搞到香港愈黎愈似啲未發展城市咁"},{"pid":"60cb7b0d9fe9b5f4ad6fef8ceb43e9a88d9ec6ef","tid":366363,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"最慘係黎多次sars 死既都係醫護人員"},{"pid":"c8b333560f6b6df574a037dc55e7562af7d0b9d0","tid":366363,"uid":69306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6df31da2876eb63a4a8e7d4fcec0c465d5315723","tid":366363,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"點解D阿叔接受到屙完尿唔洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14ea427d84de9edec172999671fba929fdfb591","tid":366363,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:03:35.000Z","msg":"其實係大陸狗多左"},{"pid":"9efc4f86189a882bd4b9f3714783478303cfbf71","tid":366363,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:04:43.000Z","msg":"廢老問題"},{"pid":"1a9d21291e07c7e28484733f611024232fae0d68","tid":366363,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽同事講，佢有親戚個女（8歲）已發燒3、4個禮拜，入私家大部分病已排除了，醫生同佢講話係叫做＂不明熱＂，我個圈子已經有兩個類似齋發燒嘅案例！<br />\n<br />\n按：病人日間鬼打冇咁精神，夜晚一、兩、三點黎燒到成40度C！<br />\n大家睇路</blockquote><br />\n唔係講笑 我媽前晚真係無啦啦燒到40度入左急症 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9506312e31ec4a96d8901d1eafe7e78fdf2b8d35","tid":366363,"uid":51233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲隨街吐痰<br />\n呢d要拉去打把</blockquote><br />\n廢老最撚鍾意 喺街成日都見到好多人吐 好似番咗大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你屌佢地，佢地會屌番你咁多事做乜"},{"pid":"374b4af45f89bcb338536a4bceb53f9cf6b81f51","tid":366363,"uid":60327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"屌 早個兩個禮拜有條廢中對撚住我係咁咳 我緊係下意識就揜下鼻先啦 佢竟然屌9我話揜咩揜啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！又話咩睇下我個袋大定佢個袋大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認我垃圾 冇即刻搏咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed4931fcac01e7695f08fb70676e5bfd52d1f80","tid":366363,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"打乞痴仲要大大力咁打<br />\n又係好撚核突同唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有D廢佬呻鼻涕落地又係痴孖根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢個大陸佬先多做"},{"pid":"aaaeb295fa955fb940a5a028ef44f2d9bf38003e","tid":366363,"uid":104033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得有必要開個post講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5月到依家因為流感而死嘅有300幾個人<br />\n呢幾個月身邊都好多人病咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得近呢兩三年 香港人嘅衛生常識減弱咗好多<br />\n好多廢老喺街喺地鐵打乞嚏都唔冚住 噴到周圍都係<br />\n其實用手臂去擋住都好啊 噴到人真係好影響到<br />\n如果真係病就戴番個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係成日見到啲人去完廁所唔洗手<br />\n呢樣野真係好撚唔衛生<br />\n摸完馬桶又剩咁污糟係咪應該洗手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨地吐痰就更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪要搞多鑊沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人永遠都要賴野去都人心惶惶嘅情況<br />\n先識去加強意識同做好預防措施 保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果班蝗黎架 無乜香港人"},{"pid":"2de301c612f8501c9999d7a45dbea81a8e701892","tid":366363,"uid":30927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"廢老去廁所唔洗手真係最濕鳩<br />\n開門個陣要掂到門柄 <br />\n搞到我洗完手又污糟返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到去要拎濕紙巾抹多次"},{"pid":"63a6d35e6588ab751c4c4ba3cf5defc1b80ad719","tid":366363,"uid":18796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人去完廁所洗手係清水洗一秒就當洗咗，好恐佈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多廢老,西裝佬唔洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柯完直接開門走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女仔好多都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34aa92ea3076ce335b97d6d665dd6dce0085597","tid":366363,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"唔係每下愈況？"},{"pid":"e6520bb692db8ce087473f56f1d1052b7bbace31","tid":366363,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得有必要開個post講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5月到依家因為流感而死嘅有300幾個人<br />\n呢幾個月身邊都好多人病咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得近呢兩三年 香港人嘅衛生常識減弱咗好多<br />\n好多廢老喺街喺地鐵打乞嚏都唔冚住 噴到周圍都係<br />\n其實用手臂去擋住都好啊 噴到人真係好影響到<br />\n如果真係病就戴番個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係成日見到啲人去完廁所唔洗手<br />\n呢樣野真係好撚唔衛生<br />\n摸完馬桶又剩咁污糟係咪應該洗手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨地吐痰就更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪要搞多鑊沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人永遠都要賴野去都人心惶惶嘅情況<br />\n先識去加強意